    "pipeline": "Founded in 1965 as part of the University of Colorado system. UCCS has grown into a regional research university with strengths in business, cybersecurity, engineering, nursing, health sciences, public service, and defense-related workforce development. The university benefits directly from Colorado Springs' role as one of America's most important military and aerospace centers.",
